Related: Product Future

Production turn inputs into outputs across time.

Production is continuous in nature, even without human intervention.

But humans consume the outputs of only a very few plants and animals.

We will replant our with those species and have food sovereignty.

We will swap skill to accomplish the work needed for that production.

We will share sources by crowd-owning the land, water rights, tools, organisms, fuel, etc.

We will use crowd funding to buy the property

Every funder becomes a real co-owner in a production arena.

All protected by the IOTA.

We will crowd-source the labor

Work toward vertical integration.

We will no longer pay interest or profit.


